own 4 live "training-resource troubleshooting MUST be root-cause code fix + harden + evolve, NOT temporary workaround"
  slug training-resource-root-cause-only
  since 2026-04-27
  scope anima training/measurement infrastructure — runpod GPU pods + HF model loaders + memory budgeting + SSH bring-up + disk allocation + dispatch wrappers + canonical helpers (tool/anima_cmt.hexa, tool/anima_runpod_orchestrator.hexa, anima-cpgd-research/tool/*, /tmp/*_wrapper.py raw#37 transients).
  rule when GPU/runpod/HF/memory/disk/SSH/version/gated-access failure occurs during training or measurement, response MUST satisfy ALL FOUR:
    (a) **root-cause diagnosis** — process state, dmesg/log signature, memory allocation pattern, exit code/sentinel absence captured (raw#10 honest); silent crashes get explicit diagnosis paragraph in verdict.
    (b) **canonical helper code fix** — fix lands in tool/*.hexa or wrapper template that prevents recurrence; NOT inline /tmp patch that vanishes next dispatch.
    (c) **defensive harden (강화)** — sentinel checkpoints (raw#80), memory probes (torch.cuda.memory_allocated + RSS), pre-flight version pin checks, retry-with-backoff guards added to canonical helper.
    (d) **canonicalization evolve (진화)** — recurring fix pattern absorbed as default mode in canonical (e.g., anima_cmt v3-default merge from v1+v2+v3 fixes 2026-04-27); ω-cycle iter leftovers get folded back, not stranded as standalone /tmp scripts.
  enforcement post-failure mandatory commit gate — failure event MUST land in repo with: (1) verdict.json + raw#10 caveat capturing diagnosis, (2) canonical helper diff fixing recurrence, (3) follow-up roadmap entry for any remaining 진화 debt; commit BEFORE next dispatch retry.
  exceptions external blockers (HF gated repo unauthorized, hardware EEG outage, RunPod region availability, account credit limit) — these are TRACKED as separate blockers (state/blockers/<slug>.json or roadmap entry), NOT papered-over with code workarounds; raw 45 omega-blocker-autofire pattern.
  bans **counter-pattern anti-actions** strictly forbidden:
    - "skip this backbone" (loses pre-registered hypothesis evidence; raw#12 cherry-pick violation)
    - "retry without diagnosis" (burns budget repeating same failure)
    - "lower n_prompts / stride / layer count to fit memory" (changes measurement protocol post-hoc; raw#12 frozen-spec violation)
    - "monkey-patch /tmp wrapper inline without canonical helper update" (canonicalization debt accumulates; ω-cycle iter leftover)
    - "bump cost cap and retry" without diagnosing why first attempt failed
    - "use bigger pod" without verifying loader pattern (vertical scaling masks code defect)
  why anima 측정/훈련은 비싼 GPU 자원 (~$2.99/hr H100 SXM × 다수 dispatch) + raw#12 frozen-spec 가설 사전 등록 의존. 자원 실패 시 임시 회피 (skip / retry-blind / cap-bump / scale-down)는 (1) 비용 누수, (2) pre-registered evidence 손실, (3) 동일 실패 반복, (4) canonical helper의 evolution stagnation을 동시에 야기. 본 own은 안전망: 자원 실패 = canonical fix 의무, 다음 dispatch는 fix가 commit된 후에만 발사. memory feedback_completeness_frame (weakest link first) + raw 45 (omega-blocker-autofire) + raw 27 (session-interrupt-recovery)와 정렬.
  proof state/v11_gemma_familyinternal/verdict.json (2026-04-27 gemma-27b OOM 정직 진단 + retry plan device_map='auto' + low_cpu_mem_usage=True) — 본 own의 첫 canonical 적용 사례.
  proof state/v11_axis96_disambiguation/disambiguation_verdict.json (2026-04-27 4 ω-cycle iter: torch upgrade → torchvision cascade → hook semantics → Pearson overflow; iter 3 residual-passthrough = 진화 debt → 2026-04-27 anima_cmt v3-default merge로 canonical 흡수) — 본 own의 정확한 (a)→(d) 4-step 적용 사례.
  proof state/v11_cmt_v3_5bb_retest/verdict.json (2026-04-27 phase1 ENOSPC → phase2 HF_HOME=/workspace/.hf_cache mandatory; canonical wrapper 패턴화) — 본 own의 (a)+(b) 적용 사례.
  evidence axis 96 6th-bb dispatch (Falcon-mamba) cost overrun 3.28× 사례 — mamba-ssm/causal-conv1d build CUDA-torch version mismatch 미해결 → 다음 SSM dispatch는 pre-pin 필수 (진화 follow-up).
  follow-up tool/anima_runpod_orchestrator.hexa에 default 'large model load template' 추가 (params_b > 20 시 device_map='auto' + low_cpu_mem_usage=True 기본 적용; HF_HOME=/workspace/.hf_cache 강제; sentinel checkpoint 매 10 layer)
  follow-up tool/runpod_resource_lint.hexa 신설 (dispatch 직전 wrapper 정적 검증: from_pretrained 호출이 device_map/low_cpu_mem_usage 명시했는지, HF_HOME redirect 했는지, sentinel pattern 갖췄는지)
  follow-up state/blockers/<slug>.json 규약 standardize — 외부 blocker (HF gated, RunPod credit limit, hardware EEG outage) 등록 SSOT로 통합 (raw 45 호환)
  follow-up SSM family pre-pin 패턴 추가 (mamba-ssm/causal-conv1d 호환 CUDA-torch matrix 사전 검증)
  category routing-dispatch
  category code-quality
